<p class="ql-align-justify">...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">招牌菜全是你没吃过的“大佬”</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">12个咸蛋黄炒的黄金蟹</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">成年人手臂大的濑尿虾</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">巴掌大的炭烤爆黄膏蟹</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">连打边炉的汤都是“黑”的</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">穿拖孩的老广都爱来！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/在法律允许范围内，以上活动解释权归商家所有/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200801/9146c845b0b14effa797550b30cfa0ac.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">CHAIRMAN GASTRONOME CLUB</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鲜活生猛的海鲜和独特的做法，俘获了不少嘴刁的老广！来的人都说：“我揸FIT海鲜真系掂，正！”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200801/043df98f16a94ed79f682cc44e433f92.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这次，【我揸FIT】把店开到了土豪村旁的<strong>天德广场</strong>，抬头就见广州塔！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>主打海鲜·打边炉·烧烤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200801/5bd2140ad7d74a3bb00c26fa3cd59d27.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">【我揸FIT饮食俱乐部】的粤菜可以说是极其优秀了，集东南亚、港澳台风味于一体！老板花了五个月时间走南闯北，只为寻找极致美味的酱料来搭配不时不吃的新鲜食材。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200801/a2a32948fb674401bf36e22523390738.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200801/16ee84119b654e98bf0a3fc64e623a08.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200801/2d070a59670741208b84a90cd74bc81d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">除了可以吃到各式海鲜之外，还有红极一时重出江湖的光头佬烧烤、广州少见的“黑火锅”！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200801/9146c845b0b14effa797550b30cfa0ac.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>生猛海鲜现点现做，个个都是大佬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">CHAIRMAN GASTRONOME CLUB</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>阿FIT招牌黄金蟹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200801/459e24dd673a42529b51454182544257.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">咸蛋黄算得上是美食界的风雨人物，只要跟它沾上边的，都会备受追捧！这不，清甜的膏蟹和咸口的蛋黄撞了个满怀，<strong>足足12个蛋黄的炒蟹</strong>，听着就过瘾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>丨蟹必须够大够威丨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200801/392791bf40ac4baa8ce956375f67c410.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">只用每日新鲜到店的肉蟹，只只生猛威风，<strong>比成年人巴掌还大！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>丨猛火爆炒才够镬气丨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200801/ec965f0140db42f3be313320c7b14be6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200801/a18fd62b10174502aebce24008aca96f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200801/dfd93c17eafe48afbd7108b8fa50a0bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">肉蟹需要先下锅油炸，防止炒制的时候蟹黄、蟹膏散开，再加入咸蛋黄一起翻滚，<strong>每块蟹肉都沾上了咸蛋黄的迷人香气。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>丨用足12个咸蛋黄丨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200801/63eab033974b4ea09f9cbf8f88f2abbb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200801/206d72717e8d496abbd6a0e03b4d6503.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>厚厚一层的咸蛋黄</strong>散发出诱人的醇香，一份合格的黄金蟹必须<strong>用足12个咸蛋黄炒</strong>，多了盖过食材鲜美，少了就不是那个味，12个刚刚好！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>丨被咸蛋黄裹满的多肉蟹丨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200801/3ce83592605c477abad8f31f7d6ef151.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>金灿灿又沙软的咸蛋黄紧紧包裹着螃蟹</strong>，试过一次你就知道什么叫无“蟹”可及！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200801/c2466a3bb033480786b6c95438cf3050.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">黄金蟹每个部分的肉都超饱满，蟹肉多到爆！入口先是咸蛋黄的咸香，带着一丝丝奶味，随后蟹肉本身的清甜渐渐浮出，这时候来上一瓶红酒，够妙！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200801/80876956372a4164bc7694a0b3ee5184.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200801/2119055d4a7a49b0befc2792755653f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">就连蟹钳也已丝丝入味，<strong>蟹肉清甜软嫩又不失饱满</strong>，一口接一口，别提多满足！香到让你吃完还吮指～</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>泰国手臂大既濑尿虾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200801/110657b831194d93a8e65b328cd6333f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">普通濑尿虾吃得够多了，试试这里的吧，我揸FIT的濑尿虾绝对会冲击你的视觉嗅觉味觉！实不相瞒，连我都惊！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>丨和成年人手臂一样大的濑尿虾丨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200801/3c4d13969fec45c3957a06358ef3af2e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">够豪横！来自泰国的濑尿虾，<strong>有成年人手臂粗</strong>，只只鲜活，你见过么？！内里满满的红膏，人生第一次怦然心动全给了这只虾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200801/733acf4f094c4b7187eb3c3c4ad8ab46.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200801/f870bcba52d34549a59b78d24e4c1573.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">呐，普通的濑尿虾在这巨无霸面前，真的是个“儿子”了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>丨神助攻般的椒盐味丨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200801/a645fdb0bc56457a96aaa348901b8d59.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200801/3211daa217fd47dfb14d95a8d624ac99.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">濑尿虾最传统的做法就是椒盐了，可以吃到食材本身的鲜甜多汁，油炸和爆炒让虾壳更酥脆，虾肉也更加入味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>丨肉厚扎实又多汁丨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200801/8f947a6d2d3147b38cacf6dc4ae90ce5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200801/8f947a6d2d3147b38cacf6dc4ae90ce5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200801/8f947a6d2d3147b38cacf6dc4ae90ce5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200801/0535d36005ac4e3c885b5716b2dba9b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">和一般的椒盐濑尿虾不同，我揸FIT的濑尿<strong>虾壳薄肉厚</strong>，一剥开内里全是<strong>超饱满超厚实的虾肉</strong>，吃起来别提有多过瘾了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200801/e0bc3dea94584dc8bdbd97f4e084c002.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200801/5391a2373a954014b91712b8aa55b4fa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>炝拌花螺</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200801/e87bae241f3646d888ac0e60d6d4e7c9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">夏季最佳下酒菜来啦~十足惹味、粒粒饱满的花螺，爽脆的口感让人完全停不下来！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200801/aac3ebeb509e4566a1739eac867c1718.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200801/a131b8cbf7c64863a254885401fcc758.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">花螺的每一寸肌肤都已经被秘制酱汁浸透，<strong>一嗦一口肉</strong>，够味！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200801/66237176cf0a4404aed607698f308f27.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200801/66237176cf0a4404aed607698f308f27.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200801/66237176cf0a4404aed607698f308f27.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200801/8d0f8c03416143d3a1d4b75e1c3f1f85.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不过我更喜欢“撸串式”吃螺，一口好几个，让味蕾完全沉浸在花螺的鲜香里！如果来上一杯啤酒，这个夏天也算圆满了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>光头佬烧烤重出江湖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200801/10b65333bf8c40f1bb85f1c68a3ad4c5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200801/10b65333bf8c40f1bb85f1c68a3ad4c5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200801/10b65333bf8c40f1bb85f1c68a3ad4c5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">除了海鲜，【我揸FIT饮食俱乐部】的其他菜也同样出彩。请来广州神级烧烤大师坐镇，过硬的烧烤功力将所有食材的风味都发挥到极致。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>丨原只炭烤爆黄膏蟹丨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200801/a12adea12a4b4cf89e3b430481f04d9e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200801/fe56c277e4d34de0930003175ff0159e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>巴掌大的整只膏蟹上架炭烤</strong>，这做法也相当壕气了！只用少许盐调味，膏蟹在一番炭烤后，外壳脆而干爽，所有的鲜甜都锁在了内里。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200801/1e795542add0418a8806e416a5e62734.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200801/1e6250bdef4140c382164d138f86e46e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200801/20f3c7ecf350404184aa1b174cd0f6e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">打开螃蟹满满的蟹膏，<strong>红彤彤地泛着油光</strong>，原汁原味吃可以更好地<strong>感受到膏蟹的鲜甜</strong>。如果蘸上蟹醋，则是另一丝别样风味，没人能抵挡得住这一口呀~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200801/9146c845b0b14effa797550b30cfa0ac.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>广州少见的“黑”火锅，也安排上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">CHAIRMAN GASTRONOME CLUB</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>广式分子卤水锅底</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200801/1a64cea4386e476faf129ce98a2c7c71.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“黑火锅”来了！<strong>独家秘制，限量供应！</strong>别小看它，数十种食材每天文火慢熬，才能成就这锅“灵魂”卤水锅底！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200801/d4a216589f6f465e90b77c474409d698.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200801/53fc40c799834860ae879062962c30ed.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200801/b68ef36536af44b8a7593edb5095933f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">浓郁的秘制卤水锅底像极了“渣男”，<strong>万物皆可涮</strong>！不管是经典搭新鲜鹅掌亦，还是鲜活的罗氏虾、濑尿虾，醇厚的酱香味让所有食材的鲜美发挥到极致！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>金汤鱼翅花胶鸡煲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200801/88ba1515f4d84aa19e71808e418f3dab.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每一锅金汤鱼翅花胶鸡煲都要花尽心思熬制，光是这口汤，需要用老母鸡、筒骨等数十种食材，文火慢煨10小时，啖啖汤都是胶原蛋白！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200801/7422d267d0ab42068ecfad2429ea0448.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">上好的鱼翅、花胶也是重头戏，每一块都很厚实，一口咬下，浓郁的胶质让你上唇黏下唇，回味绵长~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>可能系全广州炒得最好食既干炒牛河</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200801/9d531237319146148d26da2d5c3e108b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这大概是最检验粤菜厨师真功夫的一道菜了，看这菜品就知道【我揸FIT】对自家干炒牛河信心满满！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200801/21329461fe184b4cad16a07890823f6e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">干炒牛河必须得<strong>猛火快炒</strong>，这样才够烟火气！在锅与勺翻滚间，每根河粉都均匀地染上豉油，不腻口，<strong>镬气十足！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200801/7af9ba8c9a5b4b8aa6014972837b7b6e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">软嫩的牛肉和爽滑的河粉，香气如激浪般席卷味蕾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200801/9146c845b0b14effa797550b30cfa0ac.png" max-width="600" /></p>
